data.description: This loveable home features 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, oversized backyard, large covered patio, and a security system!  Beat this West Texas heat with a replaced/new inside and outside Air Conditioning Unit (2023), let the grass take care of itself with the automatic sprinkler system, while you spend time making this house your own. With a central location next to shopping centers, restaurants, and a great city park this is the ideal place to call HOME.
